This is the README file for my midterm project.
Instructions to open game:
    1.  download shortcut and all files. 
    2.  make sure to have Quake 4 installed and downloaded onto your computer
    3.  drag the pak001.pk4 folder into Steam>>steamapps>>common>>Quake4 and unzip it
    4.  Either double click on shortcut to open straight into the map OR Open the game, navigate to Mods and pick "quakeandbake"

note: the game is unfinished, only common deliverables as followed have been exectued
1. README file
2. shortcut that launches mod
3. In-game Help screen (press esc)
4. Custom UI for features (see loading screen)
5. all modified files placed in a pak001.pk4 file
